ِكَ","translation":"এরূপ ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68437,"position":2,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68438,"position":3,"arabic":"أَحَطْنَا","translation":"আমরা পূর্ণ অবগত আছি","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68439,"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয় যা","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68440,"position":5,"arabic":"لَدَيْهِ","translation":"তার সাথে ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68441,"position":6,"arabic":"خُبْرًۭا","translation":"বিবরণ","audioUrl":"wbw/018_091_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68442,"position":7,"arabic":"٩١","translation":"(৯১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":92,"arabic":"ثُمَّ أَتْبَعَ سَبَبًا","translation":"And once again he chose the right means (to achieve a right end].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2232.mp3","surahId":18,"words":[{"id":68678,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/018_092_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68679,"position":2,"arabic":"أَتْبَعَ","translation":"সে অনুসরণ করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/018_092_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68680,"position":3,"arabic":"سَبَبًا","translation":"(আরও) এক পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/018_092_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68681,"position":4,"arabic":"٩٢","translation":"(৯২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":93,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا بَلَغَ بَيْنَ ٱلسَّدَّيْنِ وَجَدَ مِن دُونِهِمَا قَوْمًۭا لَّا يَكَادُونَ يَفْقَهُونَ قَوْلًۭا","translation":"[And he marched on] till, when he reached [a place] between the two mountain-barriers, he found beneath them a people who could scarcely understand a word [of his language].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2233.mp3","surahId":18,"words":[{"id":69167,"position":1,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ",